                                                                                                               Business Briefs
                              
	 Mumbai, March 30: The Life Insurance Corporation has launched its credit cards in collaboration with Corporation Bank, which would be the card-issuer. We have launched our credit card today. The card would be like other credit cards but we will also offer value-added services like payment of premiums for our policy- holders, LIC managing director D.K. Mehrotra said.                            
	 Mumbai, March 30: Xander Investment Holding X Ltd has made an open offer to purchase a 20 per cent stake of hospitality firm Sinclairs Hotels. The firm offered to acquire 12,13,045 equity shares, constituting 20 per cent of the emerging voting capital of the target company at a price of Rs 172.50 each.                             
	 Calcutta, March 30: Allahabad Bank has signed a memorandum of understanding with the UAE Exchange amp; Financial Services Limited for inward money transfer services of the bank.                                                                                                                           
